\
\'93What was it? About your going to England?\'94\
\
\'93Yes, about my going to England. Oh, Jake! I forgot to tell you. I\'92m\
going to England.\'94\
\
\'93Isn\'92t that fine!\'94\
\
\'93Yes, that\'92s the way it\'92s done in the very best families. Robert\'92s\
sending me. He\'92s going to give me two hundred pounds and then I\'92m going\
