\
\'93Oh, you always have some one in the trade,\'94 Brett said.\
\
\'93This fellow raises the grapes. He\'92s got thousands of acres of them.\'94\
\
\'93What\'92s his name?\'94 asked Brett. \'93Veuve Cliquot?\'94\
\
\'93No,\'94 said the count. \'93Mumms. He\'92s a baron.\'94\
\
\'93Isn\'92t it wonderful,\'94 said Brett. \'93We all have titles. Why haven\'92t you a\
