\
\'93Oh, I don\'92t know. It\'92s damned useful sometimes,\'94 Brett said.\
\
\'93I\'92ve never known it to do me any good.\'94\
\
\'93You haven\'92t used it properly. I\'92ve had hell\'92s own amount of credit on\
mine.\'94\
\
\'93Do sit down, count,\'94 I said. \'93Let me take that stick.\'94\
\
The count was looking at Brett across the table under the gas-light. She\
