\
\'93If you like,\'94 Brett said. \'93I couldn\'92t eat a thing.\'94\
\
\'93I always like a good meal,\'94 said the count.\
\
\'93Should I bring the wine in, sir?\'94 asked the chauffeur.\
\
\'93Yes. Bring it in, Henry,\'94 said the count. He took out a heavy pigskin\
