\
\'93Thanks,\'94 I said. \'93I\'92ll finish the cigarette.\'94\
\
He cut off the end of his cigar with a gold cutter he wore on one end of\
his watch-chain.\
\
\'93I like a cigar to really draw,\'94 said the count \'93Half the cigars you\
