\
\'93Leave \'92em for you to finish. Let any one finish them as they like.\'94\
\
\'93It is a very interesting system,\'94 the count reached down and gave the\
bottles a twirl. \'93Still I would like to hear you talk some time.\'94\
\
\'93Isn\'92t he a fool?\'94 Brett asked.\
\
\'93Now,\'94 the count brought up a bottle. \'93I think this is cool.\'94\
\
I brought a towel and he wiped the bottle dry and held it up. \'93I like to\
