\
\'93I say. You might open it,\'94 Brett suggested.\
\
\'93Yes, my dear. Now I\'92ll open it.\'94\
\
It was amazing champagne.\
\
\'93I say that is wine,\'94 Brett held up her glass. \'93We ought to toast\
