\
\'93Hello, darling.\'94 Brett put out her hand.\
\
\'93Hello, Jake,\'94 Mike said. \'93I understand I was tight last night.\'94\
\
\'93Weren\'92t you, though,\'94 Brett said. \'93Disgraceful business.\'94\
\
\'93Look,\'94 said Mike, \'93when do you go down to Spain? Would you mind if we\
