\'93Oh, shut up, Michael,\'94 Brett said. \'93How can the man say he\'92d mind now?\
I\'92ll ask him later.\'94\
\
\'93But you don\'92t mind, do you?\'94\
\
\'93Don\'92t ask that again unless you want to make me sore. Bill and I go\
