\'93You might take up social service.\'94\
\
\'93Don\'92t be nasty.\'94\
\
\'93I won\'92t.\'94\
\
\'93Didn\'92t you really know?\'94\
\
\'93No,\'94 I said. \'93I guess I didn\'92t think about it.\'94\
