\
\'93How do you mean? They can\'92t do a thing like that.\'94\
\
\'93You try and get seats.\'94\
\
\'93Well, mother, it looks as though we better go back and get another\
breakfast.\'94\
\
She stood up and straightened her dress.\
\
\'93Will you boys keep an eye on our things? Come on, Hubert.\'94\
\
They all three went up to the wagon restaurant. A little while after\
