\
\'93You\'92re going to work to-day,\'94 I said.\
\
He nodded his head. \'93They start now, at ten-thirty.\'94\
\
\'93When do we eat?\'94\
\
\'93Huh! When do I eat?\'94\
\
He left two glasses for the bottle, and we paid him for the sandwiches\
and tipped him.\
