At Tours we got off and bought another bottle of wine, and when we got\
back in the compartment the gentleman from Montana and his wife and his\
son, Hubert, were sitting comfortably.\
\
\'93Is there good swimming in Biarritz?\'94 asked Hubert.\
\
\'93That boy\'92s just crazy till he can get in the water,\'94 his mother said.\
\'93It\'92s pretty hard on youngsters travelling.\'94\
\
\'93There\'92s good swimming,\'94 I said. \'93But it\'92s dangerous when it\'92s rough.\'94\
